# Recorded by pretext-html's scripts/build-xsl-bundle.mjs as part of its build.
# A verbatim copy of files already tracked under assets/xsl, so committing it
# would duplicate ~2.7MB in git on every upstream stylesheet refresh — and as a
# single-line JSON blob it would never diff usefully. It *is* published to npm
# (assets/ is in "files"), so `npm run build` must precede `npm publish`.
packages/pretext-html/assets/xsl-bundle.json
